longBusinessSummary: HMT Limited engages in the manufacture and sale of food processing machines in India and internationally. It offers dairy machines, including pasteurizers, milk separators, homogenizers, centrifugal separators, bottle sterilisers, centrifugal pumps, plate heat exchangers, high pressure jet crate washers, non-dairy applications, watches, oil purification, milk separator, chillers/IPHE, and clarification system. The company was incorporated in 1953 and is based in Bengaluru, India.
